The /projects/collaboration/delete API accepts requests in the following format:

DeleteCollaboratorRequest Model - Request to remove a collaborator.
projectId integer
required
example: 23456789
Project Id we want to remove the collaborator from.
collaboratorUserId string
required
example: mia-ai
User Id of the collaborator we want to remove.
Example 
{
  "projectId": 23456789,
  "collaboratorUserId": "mia-ai"
}
